    {
      "id": "6a6380f1-c3b6-4053-83a6-1d56d20c2b3b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Author uses data collected from Moodle to predict student success in a course using CART. Model focuses on detection of students at-risk based on 4 distinct activities: message exchanging, group wiki content creation, course file opening and online quiz taking. Accuracy is close 99%.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
